creator: Talking Baby
descriptionHtml:
Adopt Talking Dog as your very own baby puppy dog and help him grow into a cutest fully-grown virtual pet dog. Take care of Talking Dog, the cutest puppy out there. Talking Dog needs your love. Just talk to the talking dog. He answers with his funny voice and reacts to what you say or your touch.Customize him by choose from loads of accessories to make him look like you like!

How to play Talking Dog:
- Poke or slap Dog's face, belly, feet or hands.
- Then you can talk to Dog and he will repeat with a funny voice.
- Feed Dog his favorite foods, play with him.
- Play mini games and watch videos to collect coins.
- Tickle and slap the dog for fun.
- Have fun with talking dog on the playground and make sure he gets some sleep.
- Decorate his home and choose the best furniture to make his house look cool.
- Unlock the magical my little Puppy & Dog.
- Play as 16 different puppies and Dogs.
- Advance through levels and get fun gifts.

Enjoy hours of fun and laughter with the Talking Dog! Play now and see for yourself why the game’s so popular!
